{
  "title": "Mellow Romantic Saudi Arabian Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A romantic Saudi Arabian dish featuring lamb, pecan nuts, and lardons, with a winey and aerated flavor profile, suitable for an ayurvedic tamasic diet. This dish is perfect for a special occasion or a cozy night in.",
  "cuisine": "Saudi Arabian",
